{{see|Heroin}}
==English==

===Etymology===
Since the 1890s from a German trademark, derived from Greek ''heras'' "hero" due to the feelings of power exaultation while under the influence of the drug.

===Homophones===
*[[heroine]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

#A powerful and [[addictive]] [[drug]] derived from [[opium]] producing intense [[euphoria]] classed as a [[narcotic]] in most of the world.

====Synonyms====
*[[diacetylmorphine]]
*[[dope]]
*[[horse]]
*[[smack]]
*[[Big H]]

